nodes.title: Supir Infos
widgets_values:
With 8 GB of VRAM, the tile function should be used everywhere, use a Tile SUPIR-Sampler! High VRAM have to disabled. 
Use only the fp16 Supir Checkpoints. If you change the checkpoint, clear your VRAM!
DonÂ´t use positive Image Scale!

Steps between 32 and 128.
More S_Noise means more variation, but better results. (1.00 -1.006)
Eta check out: 
https://sandner.art/sigma-and-eta-noise-image-variations-in-latent-space-and-fast-detail-effects/
(For restoration I recommend lower values)

2 - Supir Optimize

4 - without color match

nodes.title: Info Workflow
widgets_values:
Pre-selection of the upscale models, group can also be deleted except for one node to load the "upscale model".
Or select other models and change the label of the "Load Nodes" to customize.

For restoration of very bad photos I recommend to use the restore model

Find Models with modelmanager or:
https://openmodeldb.info/
